title: Date of the contract
explanation: The text states '2002 Master Agreement dated as of May 28, 2010', which clearly indicates the contract date.

title: Party A
explanation: The text specifies 'SOCIÉTÉ GÉNÉRALE a company incorporated under the laws of France ("Party A")', clearly identifying Party A.

title: party_B
explanation: The text specifies 'CINEDIGM DIGITAL FUNDING I, LLC a limited liability company formed under the laws of the State of Delaware ("Party B")', clearly identifying Party B.

title: Specified entity Party B
explanation: The text explicitly states: 'Specified Entity' means in relation to Party B, None.

title: Specified transaction scope
explanation: The text states that 'Specified Transaction' will have the meaning specified in Section 14 of this Agreement, indicating the standard scope as per the ISDA Master Agreement.

title: Cross default applicable parties
explanation: The text states that the Cross-Default provisions will apply to Party A and to Party B, indicating both parties are included.

title: Specified indebtness includes borrowed_money
explanation: The definition refers to Section 14 of the ISDA, which includes borrowed money in Specified Indebtedness by default, and there is no exclusion here.

title: Specified indebtness excludes deposits
explanation: The text explicitly states that Specified Indebtedness shall exclude indebtedness in respect of deposits received in the ordinary course of business.

title: percentage for Party B
